            <title>[FLINK-8729] Migrate JSONGenerator from Sling to Jackson</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-8729</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The &lt;tt&gt;org.apache.flink.streaming.api.graph.JSONGenerator&lt;/tt&gt; uses Slink for JSON encoding, adding an extra dependency. All other Flink parts use a specially shaded Jackson dependency.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Migrating the JSONGenerator would allow us to drop a dependency and make the code more homogeneous.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
